Comment savoir si on a une page suivante ?
Offset pour les dates ?



https://forums.developer.amazon.com/questions/21566/linking-to-amazon-instant-videos.html


This works for me to link to a specific video in IOS:

aiv://aiv/play?asin={YOUR_ASIN}
And this seems to work for Android:

intent://watch.amazon.com/watch?asin={YOUR_ASIN}